---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Terms and Conditions">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Terms and Conditions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/90">
          Please read these terms carefully before using our services
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Content Section */}
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing and using the Dzaleka Online Service website ("Service"), you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not access the Service.
          </p>

          <h2>2. Content Guidelines</h2>
          <p>
            When submitting content to our Service, you agree to follow these guidelines:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Content must be accurate and factual</li>
            <li>No hate speech, discrimination, or harmful content</li>
            <li>Respect copyright and intellectual property rights</li>
            <li>No personal or sensitive information about others</li>
            <li>Content should be relevant to Dzaleka Refugee Camp</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>3. User Submissions</h2>
          <p>
            By submitting content to our Service, you:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Grant us permission to display and share your content</li>
            <li>Confirm you have the right to share the content</li>
            <li>Accept that content may be reviewed before publishing</li>
            <li>Understand content may be edited or removed if it violates our guidelines</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
          <p>
            We are committed to protecting your privacy. Any personal information collected will be:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Used only for the intended purpose</li>
            <li>Stored securely</li>
            <li>Never shared with third parties without consent</li>
            <li>Handled in accordance with applicable privacy laws</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            The Service and its original content (excluding user-submitted content) are protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws. Our logo, website design, and content created by our team may not be used without permission.
          </p>

          <h2>6. Resource Usage</h2>
          <p>
            Resources available through our Service:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>May be used for personal, non-commercial purposes</li>
            <li>Must be properly attributed when shared</li>
            <li>Cannot be modified without permission</li>
            <li>May have additional usage restrictions as specified</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>7. Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            The Service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Continuous, uninterrupted access to the Service</li>
            <li>Complete accuracy of all content</li>
            <li>Preservation of all submitted content</li>
            <li>Security against unauthorized access</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>8. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be effective immediately upon posting to the Service. Your continued use of the Service constitutes acceptance of the modified terms.
          </p>

          <h2>9. Contact Information</h2>
          <p>
            For questions about these terms, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Email: info@mail.dzaleka.com</li>
            <li>Address: Dzaleka Refugee Camp, Malawi</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
          <a
            href="/"
            class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-primary-500"
          >
            Return to Homepage
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* Custom styles for prose content */
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4;
  }
  .prose h3 {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3;
  }
  .prose p {
    @apply text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4;
  }
  .prose ul {
    @apply text-gray-700 mb-6 list-disc list-inside space-y-2;
  }
</style>
